# UI/UX design rules

Every component, page, or styling change must follow these rules. The AI must generate accessible, responsive, beautiful UI by default — never cut corners even if the user doesn't explicitly ask.

<!-- Ref: https://building.theatlantic.com/how-to-make-your-ui-accessible-a-practical-checklist-for-2026 -->
<!-- Ref: https://zeonedge.com/am/blog/web-accessibility-wcag-2026-aria-patterns-inclusive-design -->
